Description: A toolbox to ease the extraction and manipulaton of daily gridded climate data from a NETCDF object available from the European Climate Assessement & Datasets (ECAD) for specific time period, compute summarized values and link them to set of spatial points.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
